AnyEvent-Redis-Federated version
================================

AnyEvent based async Redis client which implements  timeouts,
connection retries, multi-machine pool configuration (including
consistent hashing), and other magic bits. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  AnyEvent
  AnyEvent::Redis
  Set::ConsistentHash
  Digest::MD5
  Scalar::Util

